that matches my expertise.

42
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:11,140
You don't want me to go with you?

43
00:03:11,740 --> 00:03:12,140
No.

44
00:03:12,900 --> 00:03:13,700
Of course I do.

45
00:03:14,380 --> 00:03:15,260
Let's have breakfast first.

46
00:03:21,980 --> 00:03:22,780
Wow.

47
00:03:24,940 --> 00:03:26,220
Did you learn all these
when you were abroad?

48
00:03:26,660 --> 00:03:27,220
Abroad?

49
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:30,980
This is a Western-style breakfast.

50
00:03:30,980 --> 00:03:32,740
So I assume you must have
lived abroad for some time.

51
00:03:33,020 --> 00:03:33,380
No...

52
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:34,340
Not really.

53
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:37,900
I'll go wash up first.

54
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:38,380
Okay.

55
00:03:53,460 --> 00:03:54,420
That was close.

56
00:03:59,380 --> 00:04:00,700
Mr. Ye, what is it?

57
00:04:00,700 --> 00:04:01,460
