an online interview.

67
00:04:14,140 --> 00:04:14,940
You're the interviewer.

68
00:04:14,940 --> 00:04:15,700
Just put on an act

69
00:04:15,700 --> 00:04:16,380
and brush her off.

70
00:04:16,700 --> 00:04:17,700
No, wait.

71
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:18,700
