94
00:04:57,940 --> 00:04:58,460
Yes.

95
00:04:59,540 --> 00:05:00,860
Is there a company you want to join?

96
00:05:05,140 --> 00:05:06,180
I want to join Jueshi Group.

97
00:05:09,460 --> 00:05:11,540
I heard Jueshi Group has a new CEO

98
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:13,900
who is nice and capable.

99
00:05:14,340 --> 00:05:16,340
He also improved employee welfare
the moment he assumed his position.

100
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:17,180
Everyone respects him a lot.

101
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:19,260
I think with a boss like that,

102
00:05:19,740 --> 00:05:21,340
