103
00:05:21,340 --> 00:05:22,260
quite promising.

104
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:23,540
Who did you hear this from?

105
00:05:24,380 --> 00:05:26,340
Our newspaper wrote
a featured report about them.

106
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:29,820
This is the kind of image
rich people love to create.

107
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:31,060
It's just one article.
Not convincing at all.

108
00:05:33,780 --> 00:05:35,340
Do you hate rich people?

109
00:05:36,540 --> 00:05:37,460
Don't you?

110
00:05:39,300 --> 00:05:40,140
It depends.

111
00:05:40,540 --> 00:05:42,100
Not all rich people are bad.

112
00:05:48,540 --> 00:05:49,140
My interview.

113
00:05:53,100 --> 00:05:54,140
Hello.

114
00:05:54,140 --> 00:05:55,300
We've checked your resume

115
00:05:55,300 --> 00:05:57,060
